[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0589","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0357","title":"Microsoft Windows 98 畸形 oshare 数据包远程拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 98 等操作系统在处理特制的 \"oshare\" 数据包时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向目标系统发送包含无效分片偏移量的恶意网络数据包，触发系统资源耗尽或崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows 98 及可能存在类似问题的其他操作系统版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0357"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.350","remediation":"Windows 98 已终止支持，无官方补丁。建议在网络边界防火墙或路由器上过滤入站异常分片报文（drop invalid fragments），阻止恶意「oshare」数据包到达目标主机。若业务允许，应尽快升级至仍受支持的 Windows 版本（如 Windows 10/11）并安装最新安全更新。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0357","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0357.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g/GHSA-3x5w-w876-g26g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0357.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0589.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0584","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0352","title":"ControlIT（又名 Remotely Possible）弱密码加密漏洞","description":"ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本（又名 Remotely Possible）存在弱密码加密漏洞，其加密算法强度不足，导致存储在系统配置中的凭据可被轻易破解。远程攻击者若能够访问受影响系统的配置文件或通过网络嗅探获取加密后的密码，可通过逆向分析加密算法还原明文凭据，进而获取系统控制权。该漏洞影响 ControlIT 4.5 及更早版本，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0352"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-25T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.740","remediation":"建议立即升级 ControlIT 至 4.5 以上版本（若厂商已停止支持，应迁移至 Symantec pcAnywhere 或当前仍在维护的远程控制方案）。同时启用强密码策略，避免使用短于 8 位的密码，并限制远程访问来源 IP 以减少爆破风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0352"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0584.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0588","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0588.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0356","title":"CA ControlIT 地址簿用户凭证弱加密存储漏洞","description":"ControlIT v4.5及更早版本使用弱加密算法存储地址簿中的用户名和密码，攻击者可通过获取本地文件访问权限或网络嗅探等手段获取明文凭据，进而以合法用户身份登录系统实施进一步攻击。该漏洞影响所有运行ControlIT v4.5及更早版本的Windows平台，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞获取系统控制权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0356"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-25","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，无官方补丁可用。建议迁移至支持强加密（如AES-256）的远程控制方案。临时缓解措施包括：使用操作系统ACL限制地址簿文件仅允许管理员读取；避免在地址簿中存储明文凭据；在网络层面限制对ControlIT服务的访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0356"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0588.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1433","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1433.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1264","title":"WebRamp M3 路由器远程访问控制绕过漏洞","description":"WebRamp M3 路由器存在访问控制绕过漏洞，即使用户在管理界面中明确禁用了远程 telnet 和 HTTP 访问功能，设备仍会继续响应来自外部的 telnet 和 HTTP 连接请求。该漏洞源于访问控制逻辑实现存在缺陷，未正确应用用户配置的禁用规则。攻击条件为攻击者能够通过网络访问该路由器的管理端口（如 23 端口 telnet 和 80 端口 HTTP）。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可通过 telnet 或 HTTP 直接登录路由器管理界面，获取设备管理员权限，进而篡改路由配置、监控网络流量或进一步渗透内部网络。该漏洞影响所有未及时修复的 WebRamp M3 设备，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1264"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.060","remediation":"WebRamp M3 路由器已停止技术支持，建议立即更换为支持现代安全标准的设备。如无法更换，可在上游防火墙或路由器上配置 ACL，仅允许受信任的内部 IP 访问路由器的 telnet（23/TCP）和 HTTP（80/TCP）端口，并禁止来自外网的所有管理访问。同时检查设备配置，确认已关闭不必要的远程管理服务。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91815321510224&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/12048","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1670","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1264.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1264","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-1999-1264.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1264.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7wj8-vvg3-vfw9/GHSA-7wj8-vvg3-vfw9.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87781/info.html","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1264.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--47eecfee-3be3-468c-b083-337bda8deecf.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1433.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0267","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0121","title":"CDE dtaction 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"dtaction 是 CDE（通用桌面环境）工具集中的命令执行组件，其存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。本地攻击者可通过向 dtaction 提交超长参数触发缓冲区溢出，从而以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响运行 CDE 的多款 Unix 系统（包括 Solaris、HP-UX、AIX 等），CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0121"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-21T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:38.013","remediation":"立即移除 dtaction 二进制文件的 setuid root 权限：`chmod 0555 /usr/dt/bin/dtaction`，阻断本地普通用户以 root 权限执行。若业务允许，建议禁用 CDE 桌面环境（`/etc/init.d/dtlogin stop && chkconfig dtlogin off` 或相应平台等价操作）。各 Unix 厂商补丁：Solaris 安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00192 对应补丁 (patch ID 107021-01+)；HP-UX 安装 HPSBUX9909-103 对应补丁；AIX 安装 APAR IY08886 补丁；IRIX 升级至 6.5.15 或更高版本。同时限制可登录系统的本地用户范围，防止非受信用户获得交互式 shell 访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0121"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0267.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0690","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0690.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0451","title":"Linux Kernel 2.0 TCP 端口拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux Kernel 2.0.36 版本 TCP 协议栈存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地用户可通过占用所有非特权端口的方式，阻止任何服务器程序在非特权端口上监听，导致系统网络服务不可用。该漏洞影响 Linux Kernel 2.0 系列版本，攻击者需具备本地用户权限，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。目前官方已发布更新修复此问题。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0451"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:25.460","remediation":"升级 Linux 内核至 2.0.37 或更高版本，该版本已修复本地用户占用非特权端口导致拒绝服务的问题。如无法升级内核，可通过 iptables 限制本地非授权用户对非特权端口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/343","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19271","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/727cf5277c8c23eaf8725829e26aff2ea619a86c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0451.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0451","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0451.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0451.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/18de81c56daca1c9e33223f0b95bdb8312a1ca75/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-px49-45qp-crhj/GHSA-px49-45qp-crhj.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0451.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/shamedgh/confine/blob/a75dad3ad336e6258a42cd1ce4af061eea68ed76/cve.files/cveToFile.json.type.csv","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0690.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0690.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0690.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0265","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0119","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 共享资源未授权访问漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 beta 版本存在权限验证缺陷，由于系统对共享资源的访问控制机制不完善，任意用户无需身份认证即可读取或删除网络共享目录中的文件。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 beta 测试版系统，攻击者可通过 SMB 协议远程访问目标主机上的共享资源，导致敏感信息泄露或数据丢失，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0119"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-19T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:37.760","remediation":"立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 beta 至 Windows NT 4.0 RTM 正式版，并安装最新 Service Pack 6a。为所有共享目录设置明确的 ACL 权限，禁止 Everyone 组具有读写权限，将共享目录所在分区转换为 NTFS 文件系统以启用更细粒度的访问控制，同时在注册表中将 RestrictAnonymous 键值设置为 1 以限制匿名访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/11"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0265.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1016","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1016.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0678","title":"Debian Apache HTTP Server 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Debian GNU/Linux 2.1 发行版中 Apache httpd 的默认配置文件将 ServerRoot 指令设置为 /usr/doc 目录，而非更安全的隔离目录。由于该目录通常包含整个服务器及软件包的文档文件，且 httpd 进程对该路径拥有读取权限，远程未认证攻击者可直接通过构造针对 /usr/doc 路径下的 HTTP 请求，读取服务器上任意文档文件的内容，造成信息泄露。该漏洞影响默认安装 Debian 2.1 并启用 Apache、且未修改 ServerRoot 配置的目标系统；攻击条件仅需攻击者能通过网络访问目标 Web 服务，无需身份认证或特殊权限，利用方式即发送普通 HTTP 请求访问 /usr/doc 下的文档资源。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0678"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.777","remediation":"建议升级 Apache 至 Debian 官方修复版本，并手动修改 httpd.conf 中的 ServerRoot 指令，将其从默认的 /usr/doc 改为独立的专用目录（如 /var/www），避免暴露服务器文档目录。同时通过 Directory 指令限制目录访问权限，禁止匿名用户读取文档文件，并移除或迁移 /usr/doc 下的敏感文档。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/318","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19253","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/cf29b986be3ae7c9144123b101d864868676099e/1999/CVE-1999-0678.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/PoC-in-GitHub/blob/e6cc3f1bf08fb0aa3b8d0e7d9611aa721f0170d0/1999/CVE-1999-0678.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0678","https://github.com/ycdxsb/PocOrExp_in_Github/blob/f24afce0dd13c7ab4ee5e40362a9ac5fc373917f/1999/README.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/6cc69bd737a75cf8d608267baabc212a8abe28cf/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0678.json","https://github.com/openbmc/openbmc/blob/11c31a44fb748171baca403be9347d7c6597c891/upstream-layers/meta-openembedded/meta-webserver/recipes-httpd/apache2/apache2_2.4.68.bb","https://github.com/DefectDojo/django-DefectDojo/blob/d9905eb7656178d3e59e0bf8f1d53a9ee9e50186/unittests/scans/openvas/many_vuln.xml","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0678.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/ef3e468e75c8d8dff11f8932eadf7d4a72af8411/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-4425-83hj-m78v/GHSA-4425-83hj-m78v.json","https://github.com/Chudry/Xerror/blob/07ec57cabcd27cdb47c89af452bdf4ed07207347/xerror/templates/openvas/reports/generic_report.html","https://github.com/lto7777777/CVE-1999-0678"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1016.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1016.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1016.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0695","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0695.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0457","title":"Debian Linux ftpwatch 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Linux ftpwatch 程序存在本地权限提升漏洞，该程序用于监控 FTP 连接时未正确分离用户权限，导致本地用户可通过 ftpwatch 程序获取 root 权限。攻击者需拥有本地 shell 账号即可利用，无需特殊权限。受影响系统包括 Debian Linux 等多款 Linux 发行版，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。建议用户禁用 ftpwatch 或限制其执行权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0457"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-17T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.190","remediation":"立即升级 ftpwatch 至 1.5 或更高版本（当前最新为 1.24+nmu2），该版本已通过将临时文件移至用户个人目录、并限制仅以调用用户身份执行检查，修复了本地提权问题。如无法升级，可移除 ftpwatch 的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ftpwatch），或直接卸载不需要的 ftpwatch 软件包（apt-get remove ftpwatch）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/317"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0695.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1375","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1375.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1172","title":"Maximizer Enterprise 4 权限许可和访问控制漏洞","description":"Maximizer Enterprise 4 日历与地址簿程序存在访问控制缺陷，当日历被共享时，任意用户均可修改其他用户的日历内容，无需额外授权。该漏洞源于程序未对共享日历的修改操作进行身份验证与权限检查，攻击者只需能够访问共享日历即可实施篡改，影响日历数据的完整性与用户隐私。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1172"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-01-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:52.400","remediation":"立即将 Maximizer Enterprise 4 升级至最新受支持的 Maximizer CRM 版本（当前已演进为 SaaS 云架构），该漏洞属于旧版日历共享功能的设计缺陷。如无法升级，应在 Maximizer 配置中严格限制日历共享范围至最小受信任用户集，并定期审计日历修改日志以检测未授权变更。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/11947","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1172.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1172","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1172.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1172.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-vm7h-v8q2-grhv/GHSA-vm7h-v8q2-grhv.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1172.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000489.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/be7ad03fdf3a412f0fd57a25f1732dc0ecfb1cb3/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1375.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1301","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1301.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1538","title":"Microsoft IIS 4（Windows NT）远程基于Web的行政管理功能存在安全漏洞，未授权用户可通过访问/scripts/iisadmin目录获取管理员密码等敏感服务器信息，导致机密数据泄露并可能引发进一步的系统控制风险。","description":"Microsoft IIS 2/3 升级至 IIS 4 时，ism.dll 文件会意外遗留在 /scripts/iisadmin 目录中，该目录未限制仅本地访问，导致远程未授权攻击者可通过 Web 访问该路径获取敏感服务器信息，包括管理员密码。该漏洞影响运行 IIS 4 的 Windows NT 系统，攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，属低危但信息泄露风险严重。Microsoft 建议删除遗留的 ism.dll 文件或限制 /scripts/iisadmin 目录访问权限以修复。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1538"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:40.317","remediation":"建议升级至 IIS 4.0 Service Pack 3 或更高版本（含 IIS 5.0/6.0），或手动删除 /scripts/iisadmin 目录下遗留的 ism.dll 文件。若无法立即升级，可在 IIS 管理器中为 /scripts/iisadmin 目录配置 IP 地址限制，仅允许本地回环地址访问，或在 NTFS 权限中移除 Everyone 组的读取权限，仅保留 Administrators 组完全控制权限。临时缓解措施：在防火墙层面封锁外部对 TCP 80/443 端口下 /scripts/iisadmin 路径的访问请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91638375309890&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=ntbugtraq&m=91632724913080&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/189","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19147","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/49836c1c79a31c6cbe258de560530ef5be1db5f4/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1538.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1538","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1538.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/36499b7630ab4a32d11ab7c901b4c87271211bec/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1538.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/iisadmin.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b1dd20ab76cf8f3afbe611ea8133362b0532868d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-9cm9-h986-74j4/GHSA-9cm9-h986-74j4.json","https://github.com/decal/werdlists/blob/81edb463f7f6311c85defefaf75ac9cd58e5cfb9/exploit-info/symantec-attack-signatures.txt","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/1xxx/cve-1999-1538.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1538.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1301.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1301.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1301.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0162","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0162.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0063","title":"Cisco IOS Syslog UDP 数据包拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Cisco IOS 12.0 及更早版本的 syslog 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者无需认证即可向目标设备的 syslog UDP 端口（514）发送特制的恶意数据包，触发系统在处理畸形日志消息时发生异常崩溃，导致拒绝服务。该漏洞影响运行 Cisco IOS 12.0.2 及之前版本的网络设备，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危，建议升级至不受影响版本。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0063"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:47:29.447","remediation":"升级 Cisco IOS 至 12.0(3) 或更新版本，该版本修复了 syslog 处理畸形 UDP 报文导致崩溃的问题。如无法立即升级，可在入站方向配置 ACL 限制仅允许可信源 IP 访问 UDP 514 端口，或在全局配置下使用 `no logging host` 禁用远程 syslog 日志记录作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0063","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19531","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ab6ab436962e16237b21ed9d4458dafc38c692fc/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0063.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0063","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/601a95d57be2a57306cd88389c2251f34b2fbcc1/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0063.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0063.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/a55bddfc5dd568e972e08b703ab596ed3580b7ba/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0063.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/49899a53e9c2e620c99e0234afe3c50e512ad851/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-h9f6-v64j-cw96/GHSA-h9f6-v64j-cw96.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0063.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5f7a9bd4-d8bb-443c-b13c-d4dc13e2ddb2.json","https://github.com/SEKOIA-IO/documentation/blob/2c5f2dacba8957b66396ed8a10bcf3d030bbc703/_shared_content/operations_center/integrations/generated/f0a10c21-37d1-419f-8671-77903dc8de69.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0162.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0629","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0629.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0392","title":"Thomas Boutell cgic 库缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Thomas Boutell 开发的 cgic 库（版本 1.05 及之前）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过向使用该库的 CGI 程序发送特制输入数据触发溢出，导致程序崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响所有使用受影响 cgic 库版本的 Web 应用程序，攻击者无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害较大。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0392"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-01-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"立即将 cgic 库升级至 1.06 或更高版本，该版本已修复 cgic 库中处理用户输入时的缓冲区边界检查缺陷。如无法升级，可在调用 cgiFormString、cgiFormStringNoNewlines 等函数前自行对输入长度做上限校验，确保不超过目标缓冲区大小。同时建议在编译时启用栈保护选项（-fstack-protector）以增加利用难度。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0392"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0629.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0680","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0680.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0442","title":"Sun Solaris 7.0 ff.core 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Solaris 7.0 系统中的 ff.core 工具存在本地权限提升漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用 ff.core 对文件的不当权限处理机制，以提升后的权限修改系统文件或用户文件。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 7.0 版本，攻击者需拥有本地访问权限，无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0442"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-01-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:24.340","remediation":"升级到 Oracle Solaris 11 或更高版本（Solaris 7 已于 2008 年停止支持，不再提供安全补丁）。如无法升级，立即移除 ff.core 文件的 setuid 位（chmod u-s /usr/bin/ff.core），并限制可登录系统的用户范围为受信管理员，以降低本地提权风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/327","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19258","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/727cf5277c8c23eaf8725829e26aff2ea619a86c/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0442.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0442","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0442.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/77fd3cf167afc5c82646a191836bcd2f9e51b459/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0442.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-48x7-62gq-cjp3/GHSA-48x7-62gq-cjp3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0442.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153100_153200.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fdbfe09c-950c-40c3-9984-4bb5f6692a41.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0680.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1437","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1437.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1268","title":"KDE konsole 本地会话劫持漏洞","description":"KDE konsole 终端模拟器存在权限检查缺陷，本地攻击者可通过访问其他用户正在使用的终端设备文件（如伪终端设备），劫持或窥探其会话内容，导致敏感信息泄露。该漏洞影响 KDE konsole 早期版本，攻击者需具备本地系统访问权限，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1268"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-01-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:04.577","remediation":"升级 KDE konsole 到包含 TIOCSPTLCK 锁补丁的版本（1999 年后的 KDE 1.x 及以上版本均已修复）；如无法升级，确保系统 umask 为 077 且 /dev/pts/* 设备权限为 600，同时建议使用 `mesg n` 禁止其他用户写入当前终端，并通过内核参数 `kernel.yama.ptrace_scope=1` 限制进程间追踪。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://lists.kde.org/?l=kde-devel&m=91560433413263&w=2","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/1645","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1268.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1268","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-1999-1268.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9b79b5eac5a874eeb91f0d9e37084feed8b830f5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1268.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-ggrx-fw3j-gvr2/GHSA-ggrx-fw3j-gvr2.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87848/info.html","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1268.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153200_153300.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000488.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1437.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url